msContents.summary: Collection of sermons dated 1707-1719, including a sermon of Thanksgiving for the Union between England and Scotland, May 1, 1707.

supportDesc.extent: 96 leaves : 184 x 119 (177 x 112) mm. bound to 190 x 120 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, i + 96 + i; 1-192, contemporary pagination in ink, upper center.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in a cursive script by a single hand.

binding.p: Contemporary leather, spine cracked, upper cover detached. Volume is fragile.
